# =============================================================================
# Tandayapa Soundscape — .gitignore
# Keep CODE + DOCS in git. Exclude raw audio, trained models, derived outputs,
# and build artifacts (all regenerable or too large / not redistributable).
# =============================================================================

# --- Raw AudioMoth recordings (device folders + any WAV) ----------------------
/F[0-9]*_A[0-9]*/
/P[0-9]*_A[0-9]*/
*.WAV
*.wav
CONFIG.TXT

# --- Trained models (BirdNET / frog classifier / Perch, etc.) -----------------
/models/
*.tflite
*.pb
*.h5
*.onnx
*.ckpt
*.pt
*.pth

# --- Derived pipeline outputs (regenerate with the R scripts) -----------------
# Keep ONLY the static-gallery template (source); ignore everything else.
/outputs/*
!/outputs/gallery_site_template/

# --- Web app build + deps (run `npm install` / `npm run build`) ---------------
/webapp/node_modules/
/webapp/dist/

# --- Rendered reports + Rmd render assets (knit from the .Rmd) ----------------
/*.html
*_files/

# --- Course material / large binaries -----------------------------------------
*.pptx

# --- Scratch / tooling --------------------------------------------------------
/work/
.playwright-mcp/
*.tmp

# --- R / RStudio --------------------------------------------------------------
.Rproj.user/
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata

# --- OS / editor --------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
